#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_animationnodestatemachine.rst:19
msgid ""
"Contains multiple nodes representing animation states, connected in a "
"graph. Node transitions can be configured to happen automatically or via "
"code, using a shortest-path algorithm. Retrieve the "
":ref:`AnimationNodeStateMachinePlayback "
"<class_AnimationNodeStateMachinePlayback>` object from the "
":ref:`AnimationTree <class_AnimationTree>` node to control it "
"programmatically."
msgstr ""

